---
title: Stovetop Chicken, Goat's Cheese and Sun-Dried Tomato Risotto with Roasted Tomato Parcel and Rocket
description: Making a risotto on the hob or stove is simpler than you think, with only three stirs needed to absorb the stock and flavours. This Stovetop Goat's Cheese and Sun-Dried Tomato Risotto also roasts tomatoes in a parcel for melt-in-your-mouth deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R43_W05_UK_R3148-18_Main_R_low-071f11d1.jpg
